  16 Oct 2012; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Remove virtual/fortran and always call fortran-2_pkg_setup as intend by the
  updated fortran-2.eclass

  08 Aug 2012; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Keyword amd64-linux, x86-linux

  21 Jun 2011; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Add dependency on virtual/fortran

  21 Jun 2011; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Added fortran-2.eclass support

  16 Jul 2010; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Remove fortran eclass use, switched to EAPI3

  20 Dec 2008; nixnut <nixnut@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc wrt bug 250370

  14 Dec 2008; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  amd64/x86 stable, bug #250370

  09 Dec 2008; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Added LDFLAGS propagation

  24 Nov 2008; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org>
  files/xfoil-6.97-overflow.patch, -xfoil-6.96.ebuild:
  Fixed patch for overflow, thanks to Joel Soete

  23 Aug 2008; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> xfoil-6.97.ebuild:
  Fixed for propagation with fortran compilers and flags, bug #235501

